&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Management Associate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you’ve always dreamt of an exciting career in Banking, Finance and Technology Services, now’s the time to make it a reality.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Graduate training, ongoing support, opportunities at leading global employers – the Alumni graduate program gives you everything you need. (And don’t worry, there’s no training bond. No exit fees, no hidden catches).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our client in Toronto is currently seeking a highly skilled Associate to join their Business Management group. This role offers the opportunity to work on cutting edge technologies and contribute to the evolution of our infrastructure.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Main Responsibilities will Include:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitoring the financial management, reporting, and analytics for the Client, Banking, Data &amp;amp; Digital Technology Portfolio.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Involvement in Fiscal year planning processes with support to development of financial demands in alignment with portfolio strategy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Presentation and analysis of all monthly and standard reporting to stakeholders.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report progress in regular meetings and through formal reporting to all groups.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish streamlined program governance &amp;amp; control for Client, Banking, Data &amp;amp; Digital Technology Portfolio, including strategic content.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with leads to facilitate the provision of timely and insightful performance data that supports strategy execution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resource tracking and headcount management inclusive of onboarding and off boarding.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work internally with the team to build a collaborative culture that drives continuous improvement and technology innovation, constructively challenging outdated and inefficient practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How the Alumni program works:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply via this job advert.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete our assessment process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get trained remotely. You’ll learn everything you need to start your career in banking services. Learning from experts from mthree who have decades of experience, you&#39;ll be taught the technical and soft skills that organizations really need. Training is completely free and there are no hidden costs or catches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Join a mthree client for 12-24 months while receiving support and salary increases every 12 months.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The vast majority then convert to permanent employees with the client at the end of the program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;University degree or equivalent.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Very strong analytical and presentation skills, with excellent grasp of PowerPoint / excel / word and ability to distill large quantities of information into key themes / issues.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal and communication skills with capacity to work with senior teams and ability to interact at all levels of the organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be able to work effectively under pressure and with multiple stakeholders and willingness to go the ‘extra-mile’.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently, multi-task, filter information and prioritize multiple demands.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experiences in budget management, forecasting and financial models is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accounting designation (CPA, CA, CGA, CMA) or MBA preferred but not required.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll get:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-depth interactive training in small

