&lt;li&gt;Understanding of the formal software development lifecycle (SDLC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of test-driven development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
